Alembic migrations for stratoclave-distill.

Run with DATABASE_URL set, e.g.

    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg://distill:distill@localhost:5432/distill \
      alembic upgrade head

The schema requires the ``vector`` (pgvector) extension. The first migration
creates it, so the database role used by alembic must have CREATE EXTENSION
privileges (Postgres superuser by default).
